		"description": "<p>Choose one of the following.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Create Water:</strong> You fill the target with up to 10 gallons of nonpotable water. Alternatively, the water falls as rain that extinguishes exposed flames in the area.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Destroy Water:</strong> You destroy up to 10 gallons of water in the target. Alternatively, you destroy fog in the area.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong><em>Cast at Higher Levels.</em></strong> For each slot level above 1st, you either create or destroy 10 additional gallons of water, or the size of the cube increases by 5 feet.</p>",
